2006年6月8日，阿奎萊拉在「{{tsl|en|2006 MTV Movie Awards|2006年MTV電影大獎|2006年MTV電影大獎}}」裡演唱〈非你莫屬〉，作為專輯的首場宣傳表演<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/ontv/movieawards/2006/|title=2006 MTV Movie Awards|publisher=[[維亞康姆傳媒電視網|Viacom Media Networks]]|date=2006-06-08|accessdate=2013-05-03|archive-date=2008-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080423094936/http://www.mtv.com/ontv/movieawards/2006/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。7月20日，她在倫敦的{{tsl|en|Camden Palace Theatre|卡姆登宮劇院|卡姆登宮劇院}}舉行40分鐘長的演唱會，演唱了5首新專輯歌跟以及2首過往單曲<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.standard.co.uk/goingout/music/what-a-night-christina-7387608.html|title=What a night, Christina|work=[[倫敦旗幟晚報|Evening Standard]]|first=David|last=Smyth|date=2006-07-21|accessdate=2014-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016100242/http://www.standard.co.uk/goingout/music/what-a-night-christina-7387608.html|archive-date=2013-10-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。8月16日，她在[[纽约州|纽约州]][[纽约|纽约]]舉行了專輯的發行派對<ref>{{cite book|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=xUwIkshfbwcC&pg=PA82&lpg=PA82|title=Christina Aguilera: A Biography: A Biography|page=82|author=Mary Anne Donovan|publisher=Greenwood|ISBN=978-0313383182|date=2010-09-16|accessdate=2020-04-01|archive-date=2020-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200709225554/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=xUwIkshfbwcC&pg=PA82&lpg=PA82|dead-url=no}}</ref>。她其後亦在8月31日於「{{tsl|en|2006 MTV Video Music Awards|2006年MTV音樂錄影帶大獎|2006年MTV音樂錄影帶大獎}}」演唱了〈傷害〉<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/ontv/vma/2006/|title=MTV Video Music Awards 2006|publisher=MTV. Viacom|date=2006-08-31|accessdate=2013-05-03|archive-date=2013-07-15|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6I7sAwrYj?url=http://www.mtv.com/ontv/vma/2006/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9月8日，她在「{{tsl|en|Fashion Rocks|時尚搖滾音樂節|時尚搖滾音樂節}}」慈善表演上演唱了〈甜心寶貝〉，並與[[艾爾頓·約翰|艾爾頓·約翰]]合唱了〈{{tsl|en|Bennie and the Jets|Bennie and the Jets|Bennie and the Jets}}〉<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1540510/beyonce-jay-z-christina-put-the-rock-in-fashion-rocks-concert/|title=Beyonce, Jay-Z, Christina Put The Rock in Fashion Rocks Concert|publisher=MTV News|date=2006-09-08|first=Farrah|last=Weinstein|accessdate=2013-06-28|archive-date=2014-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714171340/http://www.mtv.com/news/1540510/beyonce-jay-z-christina-put-the-rock-in-fashion-rocks-concert/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/57919/elton-curating-fashion-rocks-busy-with-new-cd|title=Elton Curating Fashion Rocks, Busy With New CD|work=Billboard|accessdate=2013-05-03|archive-date=2013-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130603004151/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/57919/elton-curating-fashion-rocks-busy-with-new-cd|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月11日，阿奎萊拉在「[[週六夜現場|週六夜現場]]」上演唱了〈非你莫屬〉與〈傷害〉，並跟[[托尼·班内特|托尼·班内特]]合唱〈{{tsl|en|Steppin' Out with My Baby|Steppin' Out with My Baby|Steppin' Out with My Baby}}〉<ref>{{Cite web|title=TV Review: Saturday Night Live – Alec Baldwin/Christina Aguilera|url=http://blogcritics.org/tv-review-saturday-night-live-alec/|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080526172347/http://blogcritics.org/archives/2007/01/08/101031.php|publisher={{tsl|en|Blogcritics|Blogcritics|Blogcritics}}|archivedate=2008-05-26|date=2006-11-11|accessdate=2014-02-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。阿奎萊拉亦在11月於[[全国广播公司|全国广播公司]][[圣诞节|圣诞]][[感恩节|感恩节]]{{tsl|en|Television special|電台特輯|特輯}}演唱〈傷害〉<ref>{{Cite web|title=Stars light up Rockefeller tree|url=http://metro.co.uk/2006/11/30/stars-light-up-rockefeller-tree-424411/|work={{tsl|en|Metro (British newspaper)|都市日報 (英國)|Metro}}|date=2006-11-30|accessdate=2014-02-04|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110133525/http://metro.co.uk/2006/11/30/stars-light-up-rockefeller-tree-424411/|archivedate=2014-01-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並在12月於德國電視節目「[[想挑战吗？|想挑战吗？]]」再度演唱同曲<ref>{{Cite web|title=ZDF-Programmhinweis/Samstag, 9. Dezember 2006, 20.15 Uhr, Wetten, dass..?|url=http://www.bankkaufmann.com/a-43837-ZDF-Programmhinweis--.html-Samstag-9-Dezember-2006-2015-Uhr-Wetten-dass|publisher=Bankkaufmann|date=2006-12-12|accessdate=2013-05-03|archive-date=2012-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120220052023/http://www.bankkaufmann.com/a-43837-ZDF-Programmhinweis--.html-Samstag-9-Dezember-2006-2015-Uhr-Wetten-dass|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2006年12月31日，她現身「[[迪克·克拉克的跨年搖滾夜|迪克·克拉克的跨年搖滾夜]]」獻唱〈甜心寶貝〉跟〈[[愛的鬥士|愛的鬥士]]〉<ref>{{cite web|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070106131353/http://blogcritics.org/archives/2007/01/03/094924.php|url=http://blogcritics.org/archives/2007/01/03/094924.php|title=Christina Aguilera Rocks Times Square, Launches New Single|first=Chris|last=Evans|publisher=Blogcritics|date=2007-01-03|accessdate=2014-02-04|archivedate=2007-01-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2007年2月10日，阿奎萊拉在{{tsl|en|Clive Davis|克萊夫·戴維斯|克萊夫·戴維斯}}的[[葛萊美獎|葛萊美獎]]預熱派對上演唱〈膜拜〉跟〈甜心寶貝〉<ref>{{Cite web |title=Clive Davis's Pre-Grammy Bash |url=http://www.instyle.com/instyle/parties/party/0,,1588067_1296936,00.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071209155447/http://www.instyle.com/instyle/parties/party/0%2C%2C1588067_1296936%2C00.html |first=Brantley |last=Bardin |work={{tsl|en|InStyle|時尚泉|InStyle}} |publisher=Time Inc |date=2007-02-11 |archivedate=2007-12-09 |accessdate=2013-05-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。她亦在「{{tsl|en|The Tonight Show with Jay Leno|傑哥戽斗秀|傑哥戽斗秀}}」上演唱了〈甜心寶貝〉<ref>{{Cite web|title=The Tonight Show With Jay Leno – 29th January to 2nd February 2007|url=http://www.lateshowuk.com/guest-listings/the-tonight-show-guest-listings/85/the-tonight-show-with-jay-leno-29th-january-to-2nd-february-2007|publisher=Late Show UK|date=2007-01-28|accessdate=2013-05-03|archive-date=2014-01-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140110143549/http://www.lateshowuk.com/guest-listings/the-tonight-show-guest-listings/85/the-tonight-show-with-jay-leno-29th-january-to-2nd-february-2007|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2006年底至2008年底，阿奎萊拉舉行了「{{tsl|en|Back to Basics Tour|天生歌姬全球巡迴演唱會|天生歌姬全球巡迴演唱會}}」，在北美、歐洲、亞洲、大洋洲與中東多個國家巡迴演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/1540564/christina-aguilera-reveals-european-tour-next-up-us-clubs/|title=Christina Aguilera Reveals European Tour — Next Up, U.S. Clubs|first=Jennifer|last=Vineyard|publisher=MTV News. Viacom|date=2006-09-11|accessdate=2013-05-03|archive-date=2014-07-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140715160300/http://www.mtv.com/news/1540564/christina-aguilera-reveals-european-tour-next-up-us-clubs/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。演唱會得到[[电信|电信]]公司[[Orange_(公司)|Orange]]跟[[索尼移动通信|索尼移动通信]]宣傳<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.phonesreview.co.uk/2006/03/06/orange-promotes-sony-ericsson-walkman-phones-with-christina-aguilera/|title=Orange Promotes Sony Ericsson Walkman Phones with Christina Aguilera|publisher=Phones Review. Marksway Ltd|date=2006-03-06|accessdate=2013-05-03|archive-date=2006-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20061013015332/http://www.phonesreview.co.uk/2006/03/06/orange-promotes-sony-ericsson-walkman-phones-with-christina-aguilera/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。演唱會總共演出了81場，並獲得樂評家整體正面的評價，包括讚賞演唱會為她生涯最好的演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.concerts.ws/review/Christina-Aguilera.html|title=Christina Aguilera Back to Basics Tour Concert Review|publisher=Concerts.ws|accessdate=2013-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130428003234/http://www.concerts.ws/review/Christina-Aguilera.html|archive-date=2013-04-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。演唱會於全球獲得超過9,000萬美元票房<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/news/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003685265|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100322230423/http://www.billboard.com/news/article_display.jsp?vnu_content_id=1003685265|title=The Police Score Top-Grossing Tour Of '07|work=Billboard|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|archivedate=2010-03-22|accessdate=2013-05-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成為當時女歌手第9高票房收入的演唱會，以及2007年最高票房收入的女歌手世界巡迴演唱會<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.stereotude.com/madonna/15-most-profitable-female-tours-ever.html |title=15 Most Profitable Female Tours Ever |first=Ani |last=Esmailian |publisher=Stereotude. Rev New Media, Inc |date=2010-05-21 |accessdate=2013-05-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120321024250/http://www.stereotude.com/madonna/15-most-profitable-female-tours-ever.html |archivedate=2012-03-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2008年2月，紀錄演唱會實況的DVD《{{tsl|en|Back to Basics: Live and Down Under|天生歌姬-澳洲現場演唱會|天生歌姬-澳洲現場演唱會}}》於全球各國發行<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sonymusicstore.com/store/c/Christina-Aguilera/LT_talent=1026537/TBD-Live/DVD/LT_sku=130417/ |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071012015114/http://www.sonymusicstore.com/store/c/Christina-Aguilera/LT_talent%3D1026537/TBD-Live/DVD/LT_sku%3D130417/ |title=TBD Live - Christina Aguilera |date=2007-11-20 |archivedate=2007-10-12 |accessdate=2013-05-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 發行單曲 ===
專輯的主打單曲〈{{tsl|en|Ain't No Other Man|非你莫屬 (克莉絲汀·阿奎萊拉歌曲)|非你莫屬}}〉於2006年6月6日派往美國[[當代流行電台|當代流行電台]]發行<ref name="FMQB">{{cite web|url=http://www.fmqb.com/Article.asp?id=69239#2006|title=FMQB: Radio Industry News, Music Industry Updates, Arbitron Ratings, Music News and more!|work={{tsl|en|FMQB|FMQB|FMQB}}|accessdate=2013-05-03|archive-date=2014-10-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141031092345/http://www.fmqb.com/article.asp?id=69239#2006|dead-url=no}}</ref>。單曲最高登上美國[[告示牌百强单曲榜|《告示牌》百強單曲榜]]第6位<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/57918/furtado-remains-no-1-with-promiscuous|title=Furtado Remains No. 1 With 'Promiscuous'|work=Billboard|first=Clover|last=Hope|date=2006-07-06|accessdate=2013-06-23|archive-date=2013-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130607093317/http://www.billboard.com/articles/news/57918/furtado-remains-no-1-with-promiscuous|dead-url=no}}</ref>，成為阿奎萊拉自〈[[美麗的|美麗的]]〉後首支打進榜單前10位的單曲<ref name="hot100">{{cite web|url={{BillboardURLbyName|artist=christina aguilera|chart=all}}|title=Christina Aguilera – Chart history: Hot 100|work=Billboard|accessdate=2013-06-23}}</ref>。

〈{{tsl|en|Hurt (Christina Aguilera song)|傷害 (克莉絲汀·阿奎萊拉歌曲)|傷害}}〉與〈[[甜心寶貝|甜心寶貝]]〉分別於2006年9月17日<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=09/17/2006&Format=1 |title=R&R :: Going for Adds :: CHR/Top 40 |work={{tsl|en|Radio & Records|電台與唱片|Radio & Records}} |accessdate=2014-02-02 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402110419/http://gfa.radioandrecords.com/publishGFA/GFANextPage.asp?sDate=09%2F17%2F2006&Format=1 |archivedate=2015-04-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，跟2007年2月20日作為專輯的第二首跟第三首國際單曲發行<ref name="FMQB"/>。〈傷害〉發行後最高登上《告示牌》百強單曲榜第19位<ref>{{cite journal|title=Hot 100 Billboard|date=2006-12-16|work=Billboard|issn=0006-2510|volume=118|issue=50|pages=48}}</ref>，而〈甜心寶貝〉則最高登上《告示牌》百強單曲榜第25位<ref name="hot100"/>，並最高登上[[澳大利亚唱片业协会榜|澳洲單曲榜]]亞軍位置<ref>{{cite web|url=https://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Christina+Aguilera&titel=Candyman&cat=s|title=Australian-charts.com – Christina Aguilera – Candyman|website=[[澳大利亚唱片业协会榜|ARIA Top 50 Singles]]|accessdate=2013-06-28|archive-date=2013-06-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130605144933/http://australian-charts.com/showitem.asp?interpret=Christina+Aguilera&titel=Candyman&cat=s|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

〈{{tsl|en|Slow Down Baby|冷靜點，寶貝|冷靜點，寶貝}}〉於2007年7月28日作為澳洲限定單曲發行<ref name="SlowDownBaby" />，而〈{{tsl|en|Oh Mother|我的母親 (克莉絲汀·阿奎萊拉歌曲)|我的母親}}〉則於2007年9月28日作為歐洲限定單曲發行<ref name="Swiss">{{cite web|url=https://de-ch.7digital.com/artist/christina-aguilera/release/oh-mother-2/|title=Oh Mother (2007)|publisher={{tsl|en|7digital||7digital}} Switzerland|accessdate=2014-12-17|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217160809/https://de-ch.7digital.com/artist/christina-aguilera/release/oh-mother-2/|archivedate=2014-12-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。〈冷靜點，寶貝〉發行後最高登上澳洲單曲榜第21位<ref name="AUS">{{cite web|url=http://pandora.nla.gov.au/pan/23790/20070820-0001/issue909.pdf|title=The ARIA Report – Week Commencing 6h August 2007|work=ARIA Charts|publisher=Pandora Archive|accessdate=2011-12-13|archive-date=2017-04-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170424055307/http://pandora.nla.gov.au/pan/23790/20070820-0001/issue909.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而〈我的母親〉則打進[[GfK娛樂榜單|德國單曲榜]]前20位<ref name=gersing>{{cite web|url=http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/AGUILERA%2CCHRISTINA/single?sort=entry|title=Aguilera, Christina – Chartverfolgung – Single|publisher=Media Control Charts. PHONONET (Media Control GfK International)|accessdate=2010-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141217092517/http://www.musicline.de/de/chartverfolgung_summary/artist/AGUILERA%2CCHRISTINA/single?sort=entry|archive-date=2014-12-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

